The paper discusses the use of Non-Linear Least-Squares in Robotics and Computer Vision systems, which suggests that cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also mentions the development of open-source solvers and a novel optimization system, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper discusses the efficiency of the system on embedded systems, which could fall under cs.SY (Systems and Control).
